title.rendered: Prestige Motorcars Launches The New G63 AMG Edition One.

content.rendered:
The newest member of the G class AMG family has arrived in Indonesia. Not only is it a 2019 Mercedes G63 AMG, this specific model is the “Edition One”. 

Prestige Motorcars was honoured to be able to launch the new G Wagon to the Indonesian market. Some of the differences between the regular version and this one include special interior and exterior options such as the Edition one wheels, red trim throughout the car – on the interior as well as exterior, and perhaps the most important difference – the fact that it is limited edition. 

The differences between the previous generation G class compared to this are worlds apart, despite having the classic look that  has changed very little over the years. 

Coming from the 2018 model to the 2019 one, there were only 5 components on the whole vehicle that were passed down. This is the definition of “All New” G class.  

We would just like to thank all our VIP guests that attended as well as media companies who could participate and witness the reveal of this great car. Until our next launch event!
